{
  "stem": "2539.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My name is Bronia Hatfield, B-R-O-N for Nelly, I-A.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hatfield, H-A-T for Tom, F-I-E-L-D.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bronia-- Broniaslava Goldstein, Goldstein, 'Gold-stine' actually in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it's spelled in Australia G-O-L-D-S-T-E-I-N.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, if we consider the full name is Broniaslava, then my name-- nickname or name I'm known as is Bronia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or Bronka.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born in Lublin in Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "L-U-B-L-I-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the 4th of November, 1924.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "70, exactly. 70.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in an apartment in the center of town in the [POLISH], in [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had a small apartment there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- these are my earliest memories that I have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father was never there, because my father left Lublin and went-- had a business in eastern Poland in Volyn, in a place called Lutsk, in a small town called Lutsk, which, by the way, was the capital city of Volynia.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole area of eastern Poland was called Volyn and Lutsk was at the time the biggest city in Volyn.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that meant that in Lublin, there was my mother, my sister Lola, and myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was usually a live-in woman who cooked and washed and look-- also took me to the park.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These are my childhood memories, that I went always with this Polish woman, usually, Christian woman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I only remember one, so she must have been with us for a long time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to-- she used to take me to the park every day before I started the kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, you went to a kindergarten in Lublin?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then, I went to a kindergarten, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Friedman's-- [POLISH] Mrs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Friedman's kindergarten, which was a private kindergarten for I would say select children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was a small kindergarten, small kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
